From romain at r-enthusiasts.com  Wed Apr  6 13:22:39 2011
From: romain at r-enthusiasts.com (Romain Francois)
Date: Wed, 06 Apr 2011 13:22:39 +0200
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Problem passing Armadillo objects back to R
